modName: Lakeview Manor Fish Hatchery plus opt Mill
summary: Adds a Fish Hatchery to Lakeview Manor in Falkreath. Plus an optional Grain Mill.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a Fish Hatchery to Lakeview Manor in Falkreath. Same Hatchery as the one in Windstad Manor. 

* Hearhtfire DLC REQUIRED and latest Skyrim Update
* You need to build the Apiary in order to get the Hatchery.
* Hatchery is located down the road toward the lake.
* Strongly recommend the user to use Lakeview Manor Road (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27377) *
* If you have Lakeview Manor Road load the hatchery after it. 
* Fully compatible with \"Lakeview Manor Lights,\" \"Lakeview Manor Road,\" \"Lakeview Manor Dock and Shack,\" and \"Lakeview Manor Pool and Hot Bath.\" Just remember to LOAD THE HATCHERY LAST.
author: jhdez
